metadata.title: GZMZC Dog Chain Collar with Cubic Zirconia Locking High Polished Stainless Steel Cuban Link Strong Heavy Duty Chew Proof Walking Chain Leash Collar for Big Dogs(19mm, 26")
features: Material of Silver Dog Collar: It's Hand Polished Stainless Steel chain with high strength and hardness, heavy, durable, no rust, or tarnish, ensuring many years of use! We designed a unique, attractive locking clasp with bling CZ stones. It is easy to lock and unlock the clasp and is very strong so that it can't be pulled apart even with 700lbs of force!

Size of Dog Collar: Chain width is 19MM (0.75"), and It is the best thickness for metal chain dollar. Available length are 12” to 26”. Small (12", 14", 16", 18" optional length); Medium (20", 22" optional length); and Large (22", 24", 26" optional length). Please note that this chain is NOT adjustable, measure around your dog's neck with string or tape where you want the collar to lay, and then add about 1/2 to 2inches.

Who Needs this Collar? : Do you have a dog that likes to chew? If yes, then this Collar is perfect! The luxurious Miami Cuban link chain collar looks cool on both male and female dogs. It's designed for small and medium and large active breed dogs like Cavapoo, Jack Russell, Rottweilers, Pitbulls, American Bullys, German Shepherds, Huskys, Newfoundlands, Belgian Malinois, Saint Bernards and English Bulldogs it can handle the rough breeds.

What Is This Chain Like? : When you Walking your dog this Chain is solid and heavy because it is not hollow. High polished craftsmanship makes the surface shiny and smooth and comfortable; we believe your Dog will be proud to wear this Collar. The welded stainless steel D-ring for attaching tags and the Dog's leash is substantial, and you'll never worry about it breaking.

Our Service: We believe this leash will be your dog’s lifetime jewelry because you will get a new one by free if your leash is broken down! If You Have Any Question, Please Go to Our Store Profile and Click “Ask a question”. We Cut No Corners with Our Products, and Will not Skimp on Our Customer Support to You. All items are fulfillment by Amazon, arriving you fast and safe. 100% new+ replying within 24hr.
